<bibRefCitation id="8D5E4B2C3F70FFE7FEA3FAADFDC5FAA4" author="Kovacic, M. &amp; Sanda, R. &amp; Cekovska, K. &amp; Soukupova, T. &amp; Vukic, J." box="[322,549,1323,1349]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" pagination="285 - 317" refId="ref59357" refString="Kovacic, M., Sanda, R., Cekovska, K., T. Soukupova, T. &amp; Vukic, J. (2021) Zebrus pallaoroi sp. nov.: a new species of goby (Actinopterygii: Gobiidae) from the Mediterranean Sea with a dna-based phylogenetic analysis of the Gobius - lineage. Contributions to Zoology Advance articles, 90 (3), 285 - 317 https: // doi. org / 10.1163 / 18759866 - bja 10018" type="journal article" year="2021">
Kovačić 
<emphasis id="DBBBEACF3F70FFE7FE48FAADFE3BFAA4" box="[425,475,1323,1349]" italics="true" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">et al</emphasis>
. 2021
</bibRefCitation>
), 
<collectingCountry id="91D8764D3F70FFE7FDD8FAADFD6AFAA4" box="[569,650,1323,1349]" name="Turkey" pageId="69" pageNumber="70">Turkey</collectingCountry>
, Aegean Sea (
<bibRefCitation id="8D5E4B2C3F70FFE7FCC8FAADFBD8FAA4" author="Bogorodsky, S. &amp; Kovacic, M. &amp; Ozen, O." box="[809,1080,1323,1349]" pageId="69" pageNumber="70" pagination="217 - 222" refId="ref52245" refString="Bogorodsky, S., Kovacic, M., Ozen, O. &amp; Bilecenog ˘ lu, M. (2010) Records of two uncommon goby species (Millerigobius macrocephalus, Zebrus zebrus) from the Aegean Sea. Acta Adriatica, 51, 217 - 222." type="journal article" year="2010">
Bogorodsky 
